.opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/003-skill-rename-deep-improvement/spec.md:59:Lane C build (Phase 004); doc/README three-lane rewrite beyond what the rename requires (Phase 005).
