.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/feature_catalog/04--model-benchmark-mode/01-mode-switch.md:32:| `.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/scripts/shared/materialize-benchmark-fixtures.cjs` | Materializer | First step of the model-benchmark plan, writing packet-local markdown from static fixtures. |
