.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/feature_catalog/04--model-benchmark-mode/04-mode-records-and-gates.md:18:Every state record carries `mode: agent-improvement` or `mode: model-benchmark`, so the reducer and downstream consumers can tell which path produced a record. Benchmark reports and `benchmark_run` records additionally carry `scoringMethod: pattern` or `scoringMethod: 5dim` for finer attribution within the model-benchmark path.
