.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/references/shared/promotion_gate_contract.md:51:- Verify all 5 dimensions have scores (no NaN or missing values)
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/references/shared/promotion_gate_contract.md:63:- Run `scripts/model-benchmark/run-benchmark.cjs` with target-specific fixtures
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/references/shared/promotion_gate_contract.md:67:- Verify fixture coverage (all fixtures executed)
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/references/shared/promotion_gate_contract.md:71:**Note:** Benchmark integration requires target-specific fixture set under `assets/model-benchmark/benchmark-fixtures/`. Not all targets have fixtures; this gate is conditional on fixture availability.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/references/shared/promotion_gate_contract.md:80:- Run `scripts/agent-improvement/benchmark-stability.cjs` on historical benchmark data
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/references/shared/promotion_gate_contract.md:83:- Verify no regression across runs
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/references/shared/promotion_gate_contract.md:96:- Load `assets/agent-improvement/target_manifest.jsonc`
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/references/shared/promotion_gate_contract.md:107:**Requirement:** Operator explicitly approves promotion via `--approve` flag.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/references/shared/promotion_gate_contract.md:114:**Failure mode:** `approval_gate_failed` - missing explicit operator consent.
