.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/changelog/v1.5.0.0.md:12:Packet 079 renamed the skill folder `sk-improve-agent` → `deep-agent-improvement` but kept the agent name `@improve-agent` stable, citing the original 070-sk-deep-rename precedent that agents already used modern non-`sk-` names. That left an asymmetry: skill `deep-agent-improvement` operated by agent `@improve-agent`. This packet renames the agent to complete naming-family alignment.
