.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/changelog/v1.0.1.0.md:1:Self-test, bug fixes, reducer improvements, and skill advisor routing sync for `deep-agent-improvement`. Phase 009 ran the improvement loop on the agent-improver's own definition and found a real bug (stale command path). Phase 010 fixed that bug plus 4 reducer issues and promoted the best candidate improvements. Phase 011 updated the skill advisor routing and README documentation. The goal is to make the workflow easier to follow and easier to trust.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/changelog/v1.0.1.0.md:11:- **Self-test completed** (Phase 009): Ran `/deep:start-agent-improvement-loop` targeting `agent-improver.md` itself. 3 iterations, baseline 99→100, all 5 dimensions converged at 100. First real end-to-end validation of the skill on its own agent.
.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/changelog/v1.0.1.0.md:12:- **Stale command path fixed** (Phase 010): Canonical agent-improver.md had `/deep:start-agent-improvement-loop-improver` pointing to a nonexistent file. Fixed to `/deep:start-agent-improvement-loop` → `.opencode/commands/deep/start-agent-improvement-loop.md`. Synced to all 4 mirrors.
