   170	4. Rename all 4 agent mirrors + 3 `README.txt` + `.codex/config.toml` in one changeset `[deepseek/i5 F-I5-03][minimax/i5 F-I5-03][opus/i5 F-3]`.
   171	5. Decide F-7 scope; if wide, rename command/asset-dir/state-file names + update resume/continuity readers.
   172	6. Update advisor TS + Python + graph JSON + fixtures atomically; update/remove negative penalties; update cross-skill refs + root docs.
