.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/references/scoring/lane_weight_tuning.md:106:Any "Defer" condition blocks the change. If improvements on some axes come with regressions on others, document the tradeoff in `advisor_scorer.md` plus get explicit sign-off before shipping.
