.opencode/skills/system-skill-advisor/manual_testing_playbook/05--auto-update-daemon/001-watcher-narrow-scope.md:35:> **Structure deviation note (007-deferred-final).** This scenario uses a numbered-step plus Expected Signals plus Failure Modes shape instead of the canonical Prompt/Commands/Expected/Evidence/Pass-Fail/Failure-Triage subsections. The deviation is intentional for this skill playbook category to keep scenario semantics tightly bound to runtime output checks. See `references/decisions/deferred_decisions.md` §F34 for rationale.
