.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/state_format.md:5:  - "deep-loop state format"
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/state_format.md:7:  - "atomic state"
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/state_format.md:8:  - "loop lock state"
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/state_format.md:24:- atomic JSON state writes
