.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/feature_catalog/08--council/04-cost-guards.md:3:description: "Normalizes and enforces ADR-004 defaults for max_rounds_per_topic, max_topics_per_session, saturation_threshold, and seats_per_round; computes upper-bound seat-output budgets."
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/feature_catalog/08--council/04-cost-guards.md:12:Normalizes and enforces ADR-004 defaults for max_rounds_per_topic, max_topics_per_session, saturation_threshold, and seats_per_round; computes upper-bound seat-output budgets.
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/feature_catalog/08--council/04-cost-guards.md:20:ADR-004 default normalization at session start: max_rounds_per_topic (default 5), max_topics_per_session (default 8), saturation_threshold (default 0.85), seats_per_round (default 3). Upper-bound seat-output budget = seats_per_round × max_rounds_per_topic × max_topics_per_session × avg_seat_output_chars. Guards reject session configs that exceed any cap; runtime aborts on threshold breach.
