.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:30:Every script follows the same lifecycle: parse CLI args, re-exec through the TSX loader when needed, import the TypeScript library, open SQLite through `coverage-graph-db.ts`, execute, emit one JSON object to stdout, close DB in `finally`, and map failures to exit codes.
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:44:### Stdout Contract
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:46:- Stdout is JSON-only for workflow-facing responses.
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:50:- Workflow YAML should parse stdout, not stderr.
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:59:| 3 | Input validation error | Missing args, invalid loop type, invalid query type, malformed JSON, or unexpected positional args. |
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:79:Workflow-facing fields: `graph_decision`, `graph_signals_json`, `graph_blockers_json`, `graph_stop_blocked`, `graph_convergence_score`.
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:81:Behavior: Returns `CONTINUE` for empty graphs, `STOP_BLOCKED` when blocking guards fail, and `STOP_ALLOWED` when all convergence signals pass.
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:111:Behavior: Reports clean empty state with null signals when no nodes exist.
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:136:- `SKILL.md` states direct `.cjs` invocation is the supported consumer path.
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:137:- `/doctor deep-loop` marks the DB route as mutating before snapshots or repair.
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:148:| Non-JSON stdout | Script contract drift | Restore JSON-only stdout or update YAML output bindings. |
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:149:| Empty convergence output | Graph has zero nodes | Upsert graph events before convergence or accept `CONTINUE`. |
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/references/script_interface_contract.md:157:| `scripts/convergence.cjs` | Stop-decision script and convergence output bindings. |
