.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/manual_testing_playbook/09--fanout/029-artifact-dir-override-parity.md:29:- Real user request: `Validate the fan-out YAML parity: confirm single-executor behavior is unchanged by inspecting the if_absent branch and skip_when guards, and run the full vitest suite to confirm 197/197.`
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/manual_testing_playbook/09--fanout/029-artifact-dir-override-parity.md:30:- Expected signals: `if_absent.command` = original `node -e "...resolveArtifactRoot('{spec_folder}', '...')..."` byte-for-byte; `step_fanout_spawn` has `skip_when: "config.fanout is absent"`; `step_fanout_merge` has `skip_when: "config.fanout is absent"`; full vitest suite passes.
.opencode/skills/deep-loop-runtime/manual_testing_playbook/09--fanout/029-artifact-dir-override-parity.md:44:1. `bash: grep -n "if_absent\|skip_when\|fanout_lineage_artifact_dir" .opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_start-research-loop_auto.yaml | head -20`
