codex
The implementation seam is clean: `loop-host.cjs` already centralizes mode planning, and Lane B already has the reusable executor/scorer/report pieces Lane C should copy rather than fork. The risky part is the rename: advisor state exists in both TypeScript and Python, with regression fixtures still expecting the old alias.
