+4. **Rename agent mirrors and config in one changeset.** Move `.opencode/agents/deep-agent-improvement.md`, `.claude/agents/deep-agent-improvement.md`, `.gemini/agents/deep-agent-improvement.md`, and `.codex/agents/deep-agent-improvement.toml` to `deep-improvement.*`; update frontmatter/TOML `name`, descriptions, README listings, and `.codex/config.toml` key/path. Preserve "proposal-only mutator" behavior text. [SOURCE: .codex/config.toml:21] [SOURCE: .codex/agents/deep-agent-improvement.toml:3] [SOURCE: .claude/agents/deep-agent-improvement.md:2] [SOURCE: .gemini/agents/deep-agent-improvement.md:2]
+
+5. **Update command docs and YAML without renaming command files.** In `/deep:start-agent-improvement-loop` and `/deep:start-model-benchmark-loop`, update `skill: deep-agent-improvement`, `skill_md`, and all `.opencode/skills/deep-agent-improvement/...` paths to `.opencode/skills/deep-improvement/...`. Keep command names, YAML filenames, `agent-improvement` output folders, and Lane B `model-benchmark` names. [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_start-agent-improvement-loop_auto.yaml:80] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/deep/assets/deep_start-model-benchmark-loop_auto.yaml:82] [SOURCE: .opencode/commands/deep/start-agent-improvement-loop.md:508]
+
+6. **Update advisor atomically.** In the same commit, update:
