+## Lane C implementation wiring after rename
+
+1. Add exactly one `skill-benchmark/` subdir under `assets/`, `references/`, and `scripts/`; keep shared helpers under `shared/`. This is fixed by the operator and Phase 004. [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/004-skill-benchmark-mode/spec.md:48] [SOURCE: .opencode/specs/skilled-agent-orchestration/122-deep-improvement-skill-benchmark-mode/004-skill-benchmark-mode/spec.md:54]
